Harold P. Furth Plasma Physics Library

This library is a high-density, environmentally-controlled shelving facility jointly owned and operated by Princeton, Columbia, and New York Public Library. Items housed at ReCAP are requested through the partners' library catalogs. Requests are processed daily by 3pm, and ship out to Manhattan overnight and twice daily to Princeton.
